@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-20 p-8 bg-white shadow-md rounded-xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We take the protection of your personal data very seriously and handle your information in accordance with the applicable data protection laws, especially the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-2">1. Data Controller</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
        The data controller responsible for the processing of your personal data on this website is:
        <br />
        <strong>Databox</strong><br />
        Email: contact@databox.example
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-2">2. What Data We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
        When you use our file submission service, we may collect:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <li>Your email address</li>
        <li>Submitted files and file metadata</li>
        <li>IP address and submission timestamp</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-2">3. Purpose of Data Processing</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
        Your data is processed solely for the purpose of handling file submissions, ensuring system security, and contacting you regarding your submission.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-2">4. Legal Basis</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
        Data processing is based on your consent (Article 6(1)(a) GDPR) and for the performance of a contract (Article 6(1)(b) GDPR).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-2">5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
        We retain your data only as long as necessary for the purpose of the submission or as required by law.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-2">6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data, and the right to lodge a complaint with the Austrian Data Protection Authority.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-2">7. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
        For any privacy-related questions, contact us at: <a href="mailto:privacy@databox.example" class="text-blue-600 underline">privacy@databox.example</a>
    </p>
</div>

